    "severity": "Sev-1 (Critical)",
    "description": "Long Running Job Failure incident on the Product Master pipeline (RTL_PRD_LRJF): pricing Snowflake repricing job fails on warehouse suspension.",
    "symptoms": "Full repricing DAG fails at the 3h mark when the Snowflake warehouse auto-suspends mid-query due to an idle-timeout misconfiguration on a dependent task.",
    "root_cause": "A preceding task in the same DAG left the warehouse idle for 12 minutes while waiting on an external sensor, exceeding the 10-minute AUTO_SUSPEND setting, and the resumed session lost its transaction context.",
    "business_impact": "Repricing did not complete; stores opened with previous day's prices, causing point-of-sale/ecommerce price mismatches.",
    "resolution": "Increase AUTO_SUSPEND to 30 minutes for this warehouse, or split the sensor-wait and compute steps into separate warehouses."
  },
